stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR
    
    [*] --> Draft : User submits new Node
    
    state Draft {
        [*] --> CheckConstraint
        CheckConstraint --> Valid : Only 1 Axiom?
        CheckConstraint --> Invalid : >1 Axioms detected
        Invalid --> [*] : Reject immediately
    }

    Draft --> Verified : Admin Approves
    Draft --> Rejected : Admin Rejects (Inconsistent/Duplicate)
    
    state Verified {
        note right of Verified : Visible to Public.\nConnection line is SOLID.
        [*] --> Live
        Live --> Flagged : User reports issue
    }

    state Flagged {
        note right of Flagged : Marked with Badge.\nAdded to Admin Queue.
        Analysis --> Dismissed : Flag was spam/wrong
        Analysis --> Confirmed : Flag was correct
    }
    
    Dismissed --> Live : Return to normal
    Confirmed --> DeadEnd : Mark as Dead (Grayed out)
    Confirmed --> Deprecated : Delete/Hide Node
    
    Rejected --> [*]
    DeadEnd --> [*]
    Deprecated --> [*]